    Regime-like recruitment

    regime_recruits.Rd

    Generate future recruitment timeseries based on mean and CV of distinct regimes, via a lognormal distribution.

    Usage

    regime_recruits(mus, cvs, nyears, regime_length, starting_regime, seed)

    Arguments

    mus

    vector of mean recruitment in each regime

    cvs

    vector of CV of recruitment in each regime (CVs are converted internally to log SD)

    nyears

    total number of years to resample

    regime_length

    vector inidcating how long each regime last (limited to 2 regimes)

    starting_regime

    regime to start with (0 = first regime, 1 = second regime)

    seed

    random seed for reproducability
